data.description: Nestled on a serene 2-acre lot within the sought-after Cowan School district, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home offers the perfect blend of space and comfort. The heart of the home is an expansive open kitchen and dining room with a fireplace providing a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings.  Upstairs you will find three bedrooms. The master suite boasts a private bath. There is plenty of space in the basement for extra room. Enjoy the sunroom that looks over the property. This is a must see!
